    "For instance, intervalley Coulomb scattering at momentum transfers q ∼ K is power-law suppressed at small angles [30].",
    "However, this term is important for helping to break the SU (2) K ×SU (2) K ′ symmetry to the physical SU (2) S and resolving some of the spin degeneracies of the correlated states.",
